_exptl_crystal_grow.pdbx_details    
;Under the condition of 2000 mM ammonium sulfate, 100 mM CAPS/ sodium hydroxide pH 10.5, 200 mM lithium sulfate an initial crystallization condition was identified over 3 weeks and was subsequently optimized to yield well-diffracting crystals. Final optimized conditions for YunM with SAM contained 1800 mM ammonium sulfate, 100 mM CAPS/sodium hydroxide pH 10.4, 100 mM lithium sulfate, and yielded square crystals
;
